  44:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****  ==============================================================================
  45:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****     [..]
  46:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       This driver provides functions and macros to configure and program the FLASH
  47:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       memory of all STM32H5xx devices.
  48:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c **** 
  49:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (#) FLASH Memory IO Programming functions:
  50:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Lock and Unlock the FLASH interface using HAL_FLASH_Unlock() and
  51:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****                 HAL_FLASH_Lock() functions
  52:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Flash memory programming by 128 bits (user area, OBKeys) and 16 bits (OTP and Flash
  53:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****                 data area)
  54:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) There Two modes of programming :
  55:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****             (+++) Polling mode using HAL_FLASH_Program() function
  56:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****             (+++) Interrupt mode using HAL_FLASH_Program_IT() function
  57:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c **** 
  58:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (#) Interrupts and flags management functions :
  59:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Handle FLASH interrupts by calling HAL_FLASH_IRQHandler()
  60:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Callback functions are called when the flash operations are finished :
  61:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****                 HAL_FLASH_EndOfOperationCallback() when everything is ok, otherwise
  62:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****                 HAL_FLASH_OperationErrorCallback()
  63:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Get error flag status by calling HAL_FLASH_GetError()
  64:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c **** 
  65:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (#) Option bytes management functions :
  66:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Lock and Unlock the option bytes using HAL_FLASH_OB_Unlock() and
  67:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****                 HAL_FLASH_OB_Lock() functions
  68:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Launch the reload of the option bytes using HAL_FLASH_OB_Launch() function.
  69:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****                 In this case, a reset is generated
  70:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****     [..]
